<paragraph blockId="0.[1239,2120,695,921]" pageId="0" pageNumber="222">• Smallsized marsupial with pointed snout, c. 50 reduced teeth, long vermiform tongue, and eyes near top of head; sparse, short, stiff hair on dorsal surface, softer and longer ventrally, and prominent dorsal white bands; long sparse tail hair; no pouch.</paragraph>
